01:43:28,969 --> 01:43:29,969
Shaina.

1549
01:43:30,404 --> 01:43:31,404
Cha.

1550
01:43:31,605 --> 01:43:32,605
Tòa nhà đẹp chứ.

1551
01:43:32,940 --> 01:43:33,940
Cảm ơn.

